query:
SELECT 
  p.id,
  p.orderNumber,
  DATE_FORMAT(p.orderDate, '%Y-%m-%d') as orderDate,
  DATE_FORMAT(p.invoiceDate, '%Y-%m-%d') as invoiceDate,
  p.areaId,
  a.name as areaName,
  p.isExcluded
FROM purchases p
LEFT JOIN areas a ON p.areaId = a.id
WHERE a.name LIKE '%Ward 33%' 
ORDER BY p.orderDate DESC
LIMIT 10
